data.description: Just like new in Diamond D - Built in 2019! This 3/2/2 is situated on large lot (1.07 acres) fully fenced and ready for a new family. Right as you enter there is tile throughout majority of the home with the exception of two guest rooms with carpet! Kitchen is nice and spacious and opens up with breakfast bar extension to the den/dining combo! This space is so flexible and can be made to work to your needs. Primary suite is nice in size - double sinks in the bath, along with soaking tub and separate shower. Great walk-in closet. Split bedroom plan! Great covered patio with huge backyard - full of possibilities. One owner - Seller is motivated to get this moved! Come check it out.
